Package org.locationtech.geowave.adapter.vector.query.gwql.function

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    QLFunction
    Base interface for all functions in the query language.
    QLFunctionRegistrySpi
    Class for adding functions to the GeoWave query language.
    QLVectorAggregationFunction
    Interface for functions that perform aggregations on simple feature data.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BboxFunction
    Bounding box aggregation function that accepts a single argument.
    CountFunction
    Count aggregation function that accepts a single argument.
    DefaultFunctionSet
    The built-in set of functions used by the GeoWave query language.
    MathAggregationFunction
    Base aggregation function for performing math aggregations on numeric columns.
    MaxFunction
    Aggregation function that finds the maximum value of a given numeric column.
    MinFunction
    Aggregation function that finds the minimum value of a given numeric column.
    QLFunctionRegistry
    Singleton registry for all query language functions.
    QLFunctionRegistrySpi.QLFunctionNameAndConstructor
    Associates a with a function name.
    SumFunction
    Aggregation function that sums all non-null numeric values of a given column.
